### Create a new payment
POST http://localhost:4003/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "{{sourceAccountId}}",
  "destinationAccountId": "{{destinationAccountId}}",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "type": "TRANSFER",
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Test payment"
}

### Get payment by ID
GET http://localhost:4003/api/payments/{{paymentId}}

### Get payment by reference number
GET http://localhost:4003/api/payments/reference/{{referenceNumber}}

### Get all payments for an account
GET http://localhost:4003/api/payments/account/{{accountId}}

### Get payments by status
GET http://localhost:4003/api/payments/status/PENDING

### Cancel a payment
PATCH http://localhost:4003/api/payments/{{paymentId}}/cancel

### Process a payment
POST http://localhost:4003/api/payments/{{paymentId}}/process
